					<msContents>
						<summary>

						<p>Registers the gift of a garden by purchase towards the daily offering of a big garland to Aḻagiyamaṇavāḷapperumāḷ for the merit of Iḷaiya-Perumāḷ, son of Śiṟusiṅgāṇḍai of Āḻvārkaṇmaṭṭam, who was the son of Tiruppāṟkaḍaldāsar, a <hi rend="italic">Śrīvaishṇava.</hi> Dated in the <hi rend="bold">4th regnal year</hi> of the king. The details of the date <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> <hi rend="bold">Karkaṭaka, śu. 5, Friday, Hasta,</hi> correspond regularly to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1249, July 16, Friday, ·24, ·61.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
